 would like to be able to handle the base element changing height and causing all the other element's heights too? Maybe an option?\r\nhere's a diagram of what I mean\r\n\r\n![image](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/33679961/72028421-90af0200-32d6-11ea-9002-f96d85c1182a.png)\r\n\r\n\r\nUIKit does **not** set the height of the blue card since it's the tallest card in the set. Setting the height of the blue square manually to what uikit sets the heights of all other squares fixes the issue and allows the red card to slot back to the left where it should be.\r\n\r\nCheers\r\n"},{"url":"https://api.github.com/repos/uikit/uikit/issues/4082","repository_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/uikit/uikit","labels_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/uikit/uikit/issues/4082/labels{/name}","comments_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/uikit/uikit/issues/4082/comments","events_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/uikit/uikit/issues/4082/events","html_url":"https://github.com/uikit/uikit/issues/4082","id":546328917,"node_id":"MDU6SXNzdWU1NDYzMjg5MTc=","number":4082,"title":"uk-form-custom / select / multiple","user":{"login":"timrasche","id":28338263,"node_id":"MDQ6VXNlcjI4MzM4MjYz","avatar_url":"https://avatars1.githubusercontent.com/u/28338263?v=4","gravatar_id":"","url":"https://api.github.com/users/timrasche","html_url":"https://github.com/timrasche","followers_url":"https://api.github.com/users/timrasche/followers","following_url":"https://api.github.com/users/timrasche/following{/other_user}","gists_url":"https://api.github.com/users/timrasche/gists{/gist_id}","starred_url":"https://api.github.com/users/timrasche/starred{/owner}{/repo}","subscriptions_url":"https://api.github.com/users/timrasche/subscriptions","organizations_url":"https://api.github.com/users/timrasche/orgs","repos_url":"https://api.github.com/users/timrasche/repos","events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/timrasche/events{/privacy}","received_events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/timrasche/receive