o `uk-toggle`. Like below,\r\n\r\n`<button uk-toggle=\"#invoice\" attr=\"disabled\">disable/enable the invoice field set</button>`\r\n\r\nIf `attr` is used in conjunction with `cls`, my understanding is that a target would receive toggling effects for both attribute name and class. Also, `hidden` as a default option of `attr` would not cause a break change of `uk-toggle` usage.\r\n\r\nIf someone has thought about this, please share your feedback.\r\n\r\n### Priority\r\n\r\n*On a scale of 1-5, how important is this feature to you? Please explain.*\r\n\r\n1, because I don't think this would take higher priority over committing bug fix codes. I have no idea how difficult to give a new option to a uk component when it comes to `uk-toggle`."},{"url":"https://api.github.com/repos/uikit/uikit/issues/4053","repository_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/uikit/uikit","labels_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/uikit/uikit/issues/4053/labels{/name}","comments_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/uikit/uikit/issues/4053/comments","events_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/uikit/uikit/issues/4053/events","html_url":"https://github.com/uikit/uikit/issues/4053","id":531901447,"node_id":"MDU6SXNzdWU1MzE5MDE0NDc=","number":4053,"title":"Modal and offcanvas set overflow-x instead of overflow: visible; after closing","user":{"login":"puurinternet","id":12542338,"node_id":"MDQ6VXNlcjEyNTQyMzM4","avatar_url":"https://avatars1.githubusercontent.com/u/12542338?v=4","gravatar_id":"","url":"https://api.github.com/users/puurinternet","html_url":"https://github.com/puurinternet","followers_url":"https://api.github.com/users/puurinternet/followers","following_url":"https://api.github.com/users/puurinternet/following{/other_user}","gists_url":"https://api.github.com/users/puurinternet/gists{/gist_id}","starred_url":"https://api.github.com/users/puurinternet/starred{/owner}{/repo}","subscriptions_url":"https://api.github.com/users/puurinternet/subscriptions","organizations_url":"https://api.github.