me UIkit 3 framework**.\r\n\r\nIf you like it, please give it a 👍 or ❤️  or :metal: or leave a comment , and maybe the UIkit team have this functionality in consideration. Thank you.\r\n\r\n### See it in action: \r\nhttps://codepen.io/zzseba78/full/PxwmeV/\r\n\r\n### Features: \r\n\r\n- Default and On-Off modifiers\r\n- Big modifier\r\n- Inverse style\r\n- Css only.\r\n\r\n### Possible less/sass parameters:\r\n\r\n- Width\r\n- Height\r\n- Colors ( active, on and off )\r\n- Transition: Speed, easing\r\n- Padding: space between pointer and switch slider\r\n\r\n### Tested in:\r\n- Firefox ( desktop macOS )\r\n- Safari ( desktop macOS ,  IOS )\r\n- Chrome ( desktop macOS, Android, IOS )\r\n\r\n### Things to improve:\r\nAdd text label"},{"url":"https://api.github.com/repos/uikit/uikit/issues/3648","repository_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/uikit/uikit","labels_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/uikit/uikit/issues/3648/labels{/name}","comments_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/uikit/uikit/issues/3648/comments","events_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/uikit/uikit/issues/3648/events","html_url":"https://github.com/uikit/uikit/issues/3648","id":377062868,"node_id":"MDU6SXNzdWUzNzcwNjI4Njg=","number":3648,"title":"uk-dark - misleading/confusing documentation","user":{"login":"galloppinggryphon","id":26875847,"node_id":"MDQ6VXNlcjI2ODc1ODQ3","avatar_url":"https://avatars0.githubusercontent.com/u/26875847?v=4","gravatar_id":"","url":"https://api.github.com/users/galloppinggryphon","html_url":"https://github.com/galloppinggryphon","followers_url":"https://api.github.com/users/galloppinggryphon/followers","following_url":"https://api.github.com/users/galloppinggryphon/following{/other_user}","gists_url":"https://api.github.com/users/galloppinggryphon/gists{/gist_id}","starred_url":"https://api.github.com/users/galloppinggryphon/starred{/owner}{/repo}","subscriptions_url":"https://api.github.com/users/galloppinggryphon/subscriptions","organizations_url":"https://api.github.