-6b60-11e8-898f-11732cdb512d.jpg)\r\n\r\nMy suggestion is to use a data attribute instead of href attribute (e. g. data-src), so we can use any other element instead an anchor (e. g. span, div etc). Example:\r\n\r\nCurrent with the described disadvantage:\r\n\r\nhttps://codepen.io/anon/pen/VdmJwz\r\n\r\nInstead:\r\n\r\nhttps://codepen.io/anon/pen/wXoLBQ\r\n\r\nNote: The link above only shows the suggested html code, since I do not know how to insert html code here."},{"url":"https://api.github.com/repos/uikit/uikit/issues/3427","repository_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/uikit/uikit","labels_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/uikit/uikit/issues/3427/labels{/name}","comments_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/uikit/uikit/issues/3427/comments","events_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/uikit/uikit/issues/3427/events","html_url":"https://github.com/uikit/uikit/issues/3427","id":330688575,"node_id":"MDU6SXNzdWUzMzA2ODg1NzU=","number":3427,"title":"Multiple navbar (right and left) in RTL ","user":{"login":"freefri","id":2754631,"node_id":"MDQ6VXNlcjI3NTQ2MzE=","avatar_url":"https://avatars2.githubusercontent.com/u/2754631?v=4","gravatar_id":"","url":"https://api.github.com/users/freefri","html_url":"https://github.com/freefri","followers_url":"https://api.github.com/users/freefri/followers","following_url":"https://api.github.com/users/freefri/following{/other_user}","gists_url":"https://api.github.com/users/freefri/gists{/gist_id}","starred_url":"https://api.github.com/users/freefri/starred{/owner}{/repo}","subscriptions_url":"https://api.github.com/users/freefri/subscriptions","organizations_url":"https://api.github.com/users/freefri/orgs","repos_url":"https://api.github.com/users/freefri/repos","events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/freefri/events{/privacy}","received_events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/freefri/received_events","type":"User","site_admin":false},"labels":[],"state":"open","locked":false,"assignee":null,"assignees":[],"milestone":null,"comm