ual code\r\n```\r\nvar dimensions = attr(el, 'viewBox');\r\n\r\nif (dimensions) {\r\n    dimensions = dimensions.split(' ');\r\n    this$1.width = this$1.$props.width || dimensions[2];\r\n    this$1.height = this$1.$props.height || dimensions[3];\r\n}\r\n\r\nthis$1.width *= this$1.ratio;\r\nthis$1.height *= this$1.ratio;\r\n```\r\n\r\n### My proposed code\r\n```\r\n// Sizes definition priority:\r\n// #1 tag sizes\r\n// #2 svg viewport sizes\r\n// #3 svg viewbox sizes \r\n\r\nvar svgViewportWidth = attr(el, 'width') ;\r\nvar svgViewportHeight = attr(el, 'height') ;\r\n\r\nvar svgViewbox = attr(el, 'viewBox');\r\nif (svgViewbox) {\r\n    svgViewbox = svgViewbox.split(' ');\r\n    var svgViewboxWidth = svgViewbox[2] - svgViewbox[0];\r\n    var svgViewboxHeight = svgViewbox[3] - svgViewbox[1];\r\n}\r\n\r\nthis$1.width = this$1.$props.width || svgViewportWidth || svgViewboxWidth;\r\nthis$1.height = this$1.$props.width || svgViewportHeight || svgViewboxHeight;\r\n```"},{"url":"https://api.github.com/repos/uikit/uikit/issues/3332","repository_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/uikit/uikit","labels_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/uikit/uikit/issues/3332/labels{/name}","comments_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/uikit/uikit/issues/3332/comments","events_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/uikit/uikit/issues/3332/events","html_url":"https://github.com/uikit/uikit/issues/3332","id":313442413,"node_id":"MDU6SXNzdWUzMTM0NDI0MTM=","number":3332,"title":"[Feature Request] Add uk-button-link to match anchor styles when in a uk-nav ","user":{"login":"mechanic22","id":26332509,"node_id":"MDQ6VXNlcjI2MzMyNTA5","avatar_url":"https://avatars1.githubusercontent.com/u/26332509?v=4","gravatar_id":"","url":"https://api.github.com/users/mechanic22","html_url":"https://github.com/mechanic22","followers_url":"https://api.github.com/users/mechanic22/followers","following_url":"https://api.github.com/users/mechanic22/following{/other_user}","gists_url":"https://api.github.com/users/mechanic22