d also for perimetrals items but an option to keep this items sticky to the edges could be a great added value. \r\n\r\n**SAMPLE MARKUP**\r\n```\r\n<div class=\"uk-grid-collapse uk-child-width-1-4@s uk-child-gutter-x-0 uk-child-gutter-y-5 uk-child-gutter-x-5@s uk-child-gutter-y-10@s uk-child-gutter-x-0@m uk-child-gutter-y-5@m\" uk-grid>\r\n <div>\r\n\t<div class=\"uk-card uk-card-default uk-card-body\">Item 1</div>\r\n </div>\r\n ....\r\n</div>\r\n```\r\n\r\n**STYLES**\r\n```\r\n/* no responsive gutter */\r\n.uk-child-gutter-x-0 {\r\n\tpadding-right: 0px;\r\n\tpadding-left: 0px;\r\n}\t\r\n.uk-child-gutter-x-0 > * {\r\n\tpadding-right: 0px;\r\n\tpadding-left: 0px;\r\n}\t\r\n.uk-child-gutter-x-5  {\r\n\tpadding-right: 5px;\r\n}\t\r\n.uk-child-gutter-x-5 > * {\r\n\tpadding-left: 5px;\r\n}\t\t\t\r\n.uk-child-gutter-x-10  {\r\n\tpadding-right: 10px;\r\n}\t\r\n.uk-child-gutter-x-10 > * {\r\n\tpadding-left: 10px;\r\n}\t\r\n....\r\n\r\n.uk-child-gutter-y-0 {\r\n\tpadding-bottom: 0px;\r\n\tpadding-top: 0px;\r\n}\t\r\n.uk-child-gutter-y-0 > * {\r\n\tpadding-bottom: 0px;\r\n\tpadding-top: 0px;\r\n}\t\r\n.uk-child-gutter-y-5  {\r\n\tpadding-bottom: 5px;\r\n}\t\r\n.uk-child-gutter-y-5 > * {\r\n\tpadding-top: 5px;\r\n}\t\t\t\r\n.uk-child-gutter-y-10  {\r\n\tpadding-bottom: 10px;\r\n}\t\r\n.uk-child-gutter-y-10 > * {\r\n\tpadding-top: 10px;\r\n}\t\r\n....\r\n/* responsive gutter */\r\n@media (min-width: 640px) {\r\n\t.uk-child-gutter-x-0\\@s {\r\n\t\tpadding-right: 0px;\r\n\t\tpadding-left: 0px;\r\n\t}\t\r\n\t.uk-child-gutter-x-0\\@s > * {\r\n\t\tpadding-right: 0px;\r\n\t\tpadding-left: 0px;\r\n\t}\t\r\n\t.uk-child-gutter-x-5\\@s {\r\n\t\tpadding-right: 5px;\r\n\t}\t\r\n\t.uk-child-gutter-x-5\\@s > * {\r\n\t\tpadding-left: 5px;\r\n\t}\t\t\t\r\n\t.uk-child-gutter-x-10\\@s  {\r\n\t\tpadding-right: 10px;\r\n\t}\t\r\n\t.uk-child-gutter-x-10\\@s > * {\r\n\t\tpadding-left: 10px;\r\n\t}\t\r\n\t\r\n\t.uk-child-gutter-y-0\\@s {\r\n\t\tpadding-bottom: 0px;\r\n\t\tpadding-top: 0px;\r\n\t}\t\