erhaps the lack of complete enough code samples may help explain the [Not very popular CON](https://www.slant.co/topics/150/viewpoints/20/~best-css-framework~uikit) of `uikit`.\r\n\r\n### Suggestion\r\n\r\nProvide small complete code samples in [docs](https://getuikit.com/docs/).  e.g., the `uk-tab` shows only the `tab`.  It would be helpful to show code sample of `uk-tab` and the related `content`.   \r\n\r\n```\r\n<ul uk-tab>\r\n    <li class=\"uk-active\"><a href=\"#\">Left</a></li>\r\n    <li><a href=\"#\">Item</a></li>\r\n    <li><a href=\"#\">Item</a></li>\r\n    <li class=\"uk-disabled\"><a href=\"#\">Disabled</a></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n```\r\n\r\n[foundation tabs](http://foundation.zurb.com/sites/docs/tabs.html) is an example of showing both the `tab` and `content`.  By the way, 2 or 3 (tab --> content) sets is sufficient, 6 is too many.  \r\n"},{"url":"https://api.github.com/repos/uikit/uikit/issues/2793","repository_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/uikit/uikit","labels_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/uikit/uikit/issues/2793/labels{/name}","comments_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/uikit/uikit/issues/2793/comments","events_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/uikit/uikit/issues/2793/events","html_url":"https://github.com/uikit/uikit/issues/2793","id":244498124,"node_id":"MDU6SXNzdWUyNDQ0OTgxMjQ=","number":2793,"title":"Future Request: Scrollspy Media Data Attribute","user":{"login":"reramjiawan","id":15954808,"node_id":"MDQ6VXNlcjE1OTU0ODA4","avatar_url":"https://avatars0.githubusercontent.com/u/15954808?v=4","gravatar_id":"","url":"https://api.github.com/users/reramjiawan","html_url":"https://github.com/reramjiawan","followers_url":"https://api.github.com/users/reramjiawan/followers","following_url":"https://api.github.com/users/reramjiawan/following{/other_user}","gists_url":"https://api.github.com/users/reramjiawan/gists{/gist_id}","starred_url":"https://api.github.com/users/reramjiawan/starred{/owner}{/repo}","subscriptions_url":"https://api.github.com/u